UVdata
control1A <-  UVdata$Control.1A
ppm201A <-  UVdata$X20.ppm.1A
ppm251A <-  UVdata$X25.ppm.1A
wavelength<- UVdata$Wavelength
control2A <-  UVdata$Control.2A
ppm202A <-  UVdata$X20.ppm.2A
ppm252A <-  UVdata$X25.ppm.2A
control3A <-  UVdata$Control.3A
ppm203A <-  UVdata$X20.ppm.3A
ppm253A <-  UVdata$X25.ppm.3A



#par(mfrow=c(2,2))
#Sample 1A
plot.default(wavelength,control1A, type = 'l', ylim = c(-1,1), ylab="Absorbance", xlim=c(200,900), xlab="Wavelength (nm)" , main = 'Sample 1, 1st Run')
lines(wavelength,control1A, type = 'l', col="black", lty=1)
lines(wavelength, ppm201A, type='l', col="black",lty=2)
lines(wavelength,ppm251A, type='l', col="black", lty=3)
abline(0,0,lty=4, col="black")
legend("topright", c("1 PPM", "20 PPM", "25 PPM"), lty=c(1,2,3),col=c("black", "black", "black"), cex=0.7)

#points(f.gator$snout.vent, f.gator$pelvic.width, pch=5, col="pink")

#Sample 2A
plot.default(wavelength,control2A, type = 'l', ylim = c(-1,1), ylab="Absorbance", xlim=c(200,900), xlab="Wavelength (nm)", main = 'Sample 2, 1st Run')
lines(wavelength,control2A, type = 'l', col="black", lty=1)
lines(wavelength, ppm202A, type='l', col="black",lty=2)
